    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Watch this TED Talk with Novelist Chimamanda Adichie. She tells the story of how she found her authentic cultural voice and the importance of hearing personal stories.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Video Title: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.ted.com/talks/chimamanda_ngozi_adichie_the_danger_of_a_single_story/transcript?language=en" target="_blank"&gt;The
danger of a single story&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; 18min
33sec&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transcript:&lt;/strong&gt; Available at video link above.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="max-width:854px"&gt;&lt;div style="position:relative;height:0;padding-bottom:56.25%"&gt;&lt;iframe src="https://embed.ted.com/talks/lang/en/chimamanda_ngozi_adichie_the_danger_of_a_single_story" width="854" height="480" style="position:absolute;left:0;top:0;width:100%;height:100%" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen=""&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Here are some ideas for
discussion prompts:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Did
you feel represented in the texts and videos shown while you were in school?
Why or why not?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Have
you felt singled out for being different?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Do
you believe that we are defined by a single story?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{29a08172-137a-4a33-9894-9793a2c50cc1}{122}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Go back to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@COURSEVIEWBYID*293@$#section-5" target="_blank"&gt;Try It Yourself Section&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for a list of all Try it Yourself Options.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
